

+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+
||                       SCENARIO A:  VANILLA FC INIT                        ||
||          Separate credits per FC group, single VC  (PCIe Gen1-5)          ||
+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+

 +--------------------+                          +--------------------+
 |    RootComplex     |                         |      Endpoint      |
 |     (01:00.0)      |                         |     (02:00.0)      |
 |                    |        PCIe Link        |                    |
 |PH=8 NPH=4 CplH=INF |                         | PH=4 NPH=2 CplH=4  |
 +---------+----------+                          +---------+----------+
          |                                                                   |

###############################################################################
##            InitFC Handshake (3 DLLPs per direction per round)             ##
###############################################################################
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 0 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  InitFC1-P   [HdrCr=8 DataCr=32]                                  |
          |  InitFC1-NP  [HdrCr=4 DataCr=16]                                  |
          |  InitFC1-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0] (infinite)                        |
          |---------------------------------------------------------------->> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                                   InitFC1-P   [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          |                                   InitFC1-NP  [HdrCr=2 DataCr=4]  |
          |                                   InitFC1-Cpl [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          | <<----------------------------------------------------------------|
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 1 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  * FC_INIT1 --> FC_INIT2 *                                        |
          |    (all InitFC1 groups received)                                  |
          |                                        * FC_INIT1 --> FC_INIT2 *  |
          |                                    (all InitFC1 groups received)  |
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 2 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  InitFC2-P   [HdrCr=8 DataCr=32]                                  |
          |  InitFC2-NP  [HdrCr=4 DataCr=16]                                  |
          |  InitFC2-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0] (infinite)                        |
          |---------------------------------------------------------------->> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                                   InitFC2-P   [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          |                                   InitFC2-NP  [HdrCr=2 DataCr=4]  |
          |                                   InitFC2-Cpl [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          | <<----------------------------------------------------------------|
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 3 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  * FC_INIT2 --> FC_READY *                                        |
          |    (InitFC2 received - DL_Up!)                                    |
          |                                        * FC_INIT2 --> FC_READY *  |
          |                                      (InitFC2 received - DL_Up!)  |
          |                                                                   |
          |  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *  |
          |                          DATA LINK IS UP                          |
          |  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *  |
          |                                                                   |
          |                    Credit State After FC Init:                    |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits (limit = EP buffers) --------------+           |
          |  |   P   [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8             |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 2  D: 0/ 4             |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8             |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- EP TX Credits (limit = RC buffers) --------------+           |
          |  |   P   [............]  H: 0/ 8  D: 0/32             |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/16             |           |
          |  |   Cpl [ infinite  ]  H:INF    D:INF                |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |

###############################################################################
##                     Brief TLP Demo:  MWr32  RC --> EP                     ##
###############################################################################
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 4 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- MWr32  Seq#0  [P] ----------------+                          |
          |  | DW0: Fmt=2 Type=00000 TC=0 Len=2DW |                           |
          |  | DW1: ReqID=0x0100 Tag=0 BE=fh/fh   |                           |
          |  | DW2: Addr=0x00001000               |                           |
          |  | Data: DEADBEEF 12345678            |                           |
          |  +------------------------------------+                           |
          |=========================[P: H:1/4 D:1/8]=======================>> |
          |                                   Absorbed MWr: 2DW @ 0x00001000  |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits (after 1 MWr) ---------------------+           |
          |  |   P   [###.........]  H: 1/ 4  D: 1/ 8             |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 2  D: 0/ 4             |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8             |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |


+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+
||                        SCENARIO B:  MERGED CREDITS                        ||
||         P & Cpl share a single pool across VC0+VC1;  NP is per-VC         ||
+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+

 +--------------------+                          +--------------------+
 |    RootComplex     |                         |      Endpoint      |
 |     (01:00.0)      |                         |     (02:00.0)      |
 |                    |        PCIe Link        |                    |
 |P:merged Cpl:merged |                         |P:merged Cpl:merged |
 +---------+----------+                          +---------+----------+
          |                                                                   |

###############################################################################
##        InitFC Handshake (6 DLLPs/dir: 3 groups x 2 VCs per round)         ##
###############################################################################
          |                                                                   |
          |     VC0 carries total shared pool for merged groups (P, Cpl).     |
          |     VC1 carries 0/0 for merged groups = 'I share VC0's pool'.     |
          |                  NP remains independent per VC.                   |
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 0 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  [VC0] InitFC1-P   [HdrCr=8 DataCr=32]                            |
          |  [VC0] InitFC1-NP  [HdrCr=4 DataCr=16]                            |
          |  [VC0] InitFC1-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]                             |
          |---------------------------------------------------------------->> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                             [VC0] InitFC1-P   [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          |                             [VC0] InitFC1-NP  [HdrCr=2 DataCr=4]  |
          |                             [VC0] InitFC1-Cpl [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          | <<----------------------------------------------------------------|
          |                                                                   |
          |  [VC1] InitFC1-P   [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]                             |
          |  [VC1] InitFC1-NP  [HdrCr=2 DataCr=8]                             |
          |  [VC1] InitFC1-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]                             |
          |---------------------------------------------------------------->> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                             [VC1] InitFC1-P   [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]  |
          |                             [VC1] InitFC1-NP  [HdrCr=1 DataCr=2]  |
          |                             [VC1] InitFC1-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]  |
          | <<----------------------------------------------------------------|
          |                                                                   |
          |  VC0 P/Cpl: total shared pool sizes                               |
          |  VC1 P=0/Cpl=0: merged (NOT infinite!)                            |
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 1 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  * FC_INIT1 --> FC_INIT2 *                                        |
          |    (all InitFC1 groups received)                                  |
          |                                        * FC_INIT1 --> FC_INIT2 *  |
          |                                    (all InitFC1 groups received)  |
==========+======================== CYCLE 2 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  [VC0] InitFC2-P   [HdrCr=8 DataCr=32]                            |
          |  [VC0] InitFC2-NP  [HdrCr=4 DataCr=16]                            |
          |  [VC0] InitFC2-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]                             |
          |---------------------------------------------------------------->> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                             [VC0] InitFC2-P   [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          |                             [VC0] InitFC2-NP  [HdrCr=2 DataCr=4]  |
          |                             [VC0] InitFC2-Cpl [HdrCr=4 DataCr=8]  |
          | <<----------------------------------------------------------------|
          |                                                                   |
          |  [VC1] InitFC2-P   [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]                             |
          |  [VC1] InitFC2-NP  [HdrCr=2 DataCr=8]                             |
          |  [VC1] InitFC2-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]                             |
          |---------------------------------------------------------------->> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                             [VC1] InitFC2-P   [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]  |
          |                             [VC1] InitFC2-NP  [HdrCr=1 DataCr=2]  |
          |                             [VC1] InitFC2-Cpl [HdrCr=0 DataCr=0]  |
          | <<----------------------------------------------------------------|
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 3 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  * FC_INIT2 --> FC_READY *                                        |
          |    (InitFC2 received - DL_Up!)                                    |
          |                                        * FC_INIT2 --> FC_READY *  |
          |                                      (InitFC2 received - DL_Up!)  |
          |                                                                   |
          |  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *  |
          |                          DATA LINK IS UP                          |
          |  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *  |
          |                                                                   |
          |                    Credit State After FC Init:                    |
          |         (P and Cpl show SAME shared tracker for both VCs)         |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits -- VC0 view -----------------------+           |
          |  |   P   [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 2  D: 0/ 4 (VC0)       |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits -- VC1 view -----------------------+           |
          |  |   P   [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 1  D: 0/ 2 (VC1)       |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |

###############################################################################
##             Shared Credit Demo:  MWr32 on VC0 affects VC1 too             ##
###############################################################################
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 4 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- MWr32  Seq#0  [P] ----------------+                          |
          |  | DW0: Fmt=2 Type=00000 TC=0 Len=2DW |                           |
          |  | DW1: ReqID=0x0100 Tag=0 BE=fh/fh   |                           |
          |  | DW2: Addr=0x00001000               |                           |
          |  | Data: AAAABBBB CCCCDDDD            |                           |
          |  +------------------------------------+                           |
          |=========================[P: H:1/4 D:1/8]=======================>> |
          |                                   Absorbed MWr: 2DW @ 0x00001000  |
          |                                                                   |
          |   After MWr on VC0 — shared P credits consumed for BOTH VCs:    |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits -- VC0 view -----------------------+           |
          |  |   P   [###.........]  H: 1/ 4  D: 1/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 2  D: 0/ 4 (VC0)       |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits -- VC1 view -----------------------+           |
          |  |   P   [###.........]  H: 1/ 4  D: 1/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 1  D: 0/ 2 (VC1)       |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8 (shared)    |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |
          |         ^ P row is IDENTICAL in both views (shared pool)          |
          |                 NP row differs (independent per VC)               |
          |                                                                   |


+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+
||                      SCENARIO C:  FLIT MODE FC INIT                       ||
||         PCIe 6.0+ -- 256B flits, no DLLPs, all credits in 1 flit          ||
+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+

 +--------------------+                          +--------------------+
 |    RootComplex     |                         |      Endpoint      |
 |     (01:00.0)      |                         |     (02:00.0)      |
 |                    |        PCIe Link        |                    |
 |PH=16 NPH=8 CplH=INF|                         | PH=8  NPH=4 CplH=8 |
 +---------+----------+                          +---------+----------+
          |                                                                   |

###############################################################################
##           Flit-Based FC Init (1 flit/dir carries ALL 3 groups)            ##
###############################################################################
          |                                                                   |
          |    Key difference: NO DLLPs at all. FC info embedded in flit.     |
          |    One 256B flit replaces three separate ~8B DLLPs per round.     |
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 0 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  +--- FC-Init-1  Seq#0  [256B Flit] ------------+                 |
          |  | All 3 FC groups in a single flit (no DLLPs) |                  |
          |  | Posted:     HdrCr=16  DataCr=64             |                  |
          |  | NonPosted:  HdrCr=8  DataCr=32              |                  |
          |  | Completion: HdrCr=0  DataCr=0  (infinite)   |                  |
          |  +---------------------------------------------+                  |
          |============================[256B FLIT]=========================>> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                  +--- FC-Init-1  Seq#0  [256B Flit] ------------+ |
          |                  | All 3 FC groups in a single flit (no DLLPs) |  |
          |                  | Posted:     HdrCr=8  DataCr=16              |  |
          |                  | NonPosted:  HdrCr=4  DataCr=8               |  |
          |                  | Completion: HdrCr=8  DataCr=16              |  |
          |                  +---------------------------------------------+  |
          | <<=========================[256B FLIT]============================|
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 1 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  * FC_INIT1 --> FC_INIT2 *                                        |
          |    (all InitFC1 groups received)                                  |
          |                                        * FC_INIT1 --> FC_INIT2 *  |
          |                                    (all InitFC1 groups received)  |
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 2 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  +--- FC-Init-2  Seq#1  [256B Flit] ------------+                 |
          |  | All 3 FC groups in a single flit (no DLLPs) |                  |
          |  | Posted:     HdrCr=16  DataCr=64             |                  |
          |  | NonPosted:  HdrCr=8  DataCr=32              |                  |
          |  | Completion: HdrCr=0  DataCr=0  (infinite)   |                  |
          |  +---------------------------------------------+                  |
          |============================[256B FLIT]=========================>> |
          |                                                                   |
          |                  +--- FC-Init-2  Seq#1  [256B Flit] ------------+ |
          |                  | All 3 FC groups in a single flit (no DLLPs) |  |
          |                  | Posted:     HdrCr=8  DataCr=16              |  |
          |                  | NonPosted:  HdrCr=4  DataCr=8               |  |
          |                  | Completion: HdrCr=8  DataCr=16              |  |
          |                  +---------------------------------------------+  |
          | <<=========================[256B FLIT]============================|
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 3 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  * FC_INIT2 --> FC_READY *                                        |
          |    (InitFC2 received - DL_Up!)                                    |
          |                                        * FC_INIT2 --> FC_READY *  |
          |                                      (InitFC2 received - DL_Up!)  |
          |                                                                   |
          |  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *  |
          |                          DATA LINK IS UP                          |
          |  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *  |
          |                                                                   |
          |               Credit State After Flit-Mode FC Init:               |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits (limit = EP buffers) --------------+           |
          |  |   P   [............]  H: 0/ 8  D: 0/16             |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8             |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 8  D: 0/16             |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- EP TX Credits (limit = RC buffers) --------------+           |
          |  |   P   [............]  H: 0/16  D: 0/64             |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 8  D: 0/32             |           |
          |  |   Cpl [ infinite  ]  H:INF    D:INF                |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |

###############################################################################
##          Brief TLP Demo:  MWr32  RC --> EP  (packed inside flit)          ##
###############################################################################
          |                                                                   |
          |      In flit mode, TLPs are packed into 256B flit payloads.       |
          |             Credit tracking still works per FC group.             |
          |                                                                   |
==========+======================== CYCLE 4 ==================================+
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- MWr32  Seq#2  [P] -----------------------+                   |
          |  | DW0: Fmt=2 Type=00000 TC=0 Len=4DW        |                    |
          |  | DW1: ReqID=0x0100 Tag=0 BE=fh/fh          |                    |
          |  | DW2: Addr=0x00005000                      |                    |
          |  | Data: F1F1F1F1 E2E2E2E2 D3D3D3D3 C4C4C4C4 |                    |
          |  +-------------------------------------------+                    |
          |=========================[P: H:1/8 D:1/16]======================>> |
          |                                   Absorbed MWr: 4DW @ 0x00005000  |
          |                                                                   |
          |  +-- RC TX Credits (after 1 MWr) ---------------------+           |
          |  |   P   [#...........]  H: 1/ 8  D: 1/16             |           |
          |  |   NP  [............]  H: 0/ 4  D: 0/ 8             |           |
          |  |   Cpl [............]  H: 0/ 8  D: 0/16             |           |
          |  +----------------------------------------------------+           |
          |                                                                   |


+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+
||                            COMPARISON SUMMARY                             ||
||                   How the three FC init flavors differ                    ||
+=============================================================================+
+=============================================================================+

          |     +-------------------------------------------------------+     |
          |     |              |  Vanilla   | Merged Cr. | Flit Mode    |     |
          |     +-------------------------------------------------------+     |
          |     | Wire format  |  DLLPs     |  DLLPs     | 256B Flits   |     |
          |     | Pkts/round   |  3 (P/NP/C)|  6 (x2 VC) | 1 flit       |     |
          |     | Credit pools |  per-VC    |  shared P/C| per-VC       |     |
          |     | VCs shown    |  VC0 only  |  VC0 + VC1 | VC0 only     |     |
          |     | VC1 P=0 mean |  (n/a)     |  merged    | (n/a)        |     |
          |     | DLLPs exist? |  Yes       |  Yes       | No           |     |
          |     | PCIe Gen     |  1-5       |  1-5       | 6.0+         |     |
          |     +-------------------------------------------------------+     |
          |                                                                   |
          |                  Full log saved to: pcie_sim.log                  |
          |                                                                   |
